snippet.title: Info Gamer
snippet.description:
The best way to get the most out of this channel is to become a member on our website https://www.infogamerhub.com/memberships/

We build popular and once-popular games to show what steps they might have used. We also want to start making lots of game assets with Blender and Maya. We can't build out this channel without you so please share and subscribe to our content. We get better everyday and we want you guys to get better also. Come and build games with us. We have lots of plans in the future to make this channel the go-to channel in entertainment and learning. Let's do this drop a like and subscribe and let's become game-making superstars. Thanks again guys seriously we need your help in the development of this channel. Lets code, script, draw and create awesome video games
